OL,3,C'I was just a drunk idiot' - Men face
OL,4,C'day of reckoning' after violent scenes
OL,6,FThree more people have been sentenced
OL,7,Fafter a week of violence and unrest
OL,8,Facross the West Country.
OL,10,FA pair of men have pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fviolent disorder after widespread
OL,12,Funrest in Bristol on Saturday.
OL,14,FMark Bowen, 40, of no fixed abode, and
OL,15,FDaniel Russell, 47, of Redfield,
OL,16,Fappeared separately before Bristol
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court on Friday 8 August.
