OL,3,C'I was just a drunk idiot' - Men face
OL,4,C'day of reckoning' after violent scenes
OL,6,FBoth admitted the single charge
OL,7,Fagainst them and were remanded in
OL,8,Fcustody ahead of their sentencing
OL,9,Fhearing at Bristol Crown Court on
OL,10,FWednesday 14 August.
OL,12,FThe court heard how Mr Bowen told
OL,13,Fofficers when he was arrested "I
OL,14,Fdidn't even know what was going on, I
OL,15,Fdon't have social media, I was just a
OL,16,Fdrunk idiot."
OL,18,FJudge Lynne Matthews said to Mr
OL,19,FRussell: "You will appear for your day
OL,20,Fof reckoning at Bristol Crown Court."
