OL,6,FIt follows clashes between anti-
OL,7,Fimmigration demonstrators and counter-
OL,8,Fprotesters on Saturday.
OL,10,FRumours circulated of a second right-
OL,11,Fwing protest on Wednesday, but instead
OL,12,Fthousands of anti racism protestors
OL,13,Fflooded the streets of Bristol in a
OL,14,Fpeaceful rally.
