OL,3,C'I was just a drunk idiot' - Men face
OL,4,C'day of reckoning' after violent scenes
OL,6,FA vandal who caused thousands of
OL,7,Fpounds worth of damage to a high
OL,8,Fstreet store has been jailed four days
OL,9,Fafter violent disorder broke out in
OL,10,FPlymouth City Centre.
OL,12,FJustin Crimp, 49, was identified after
OL,13,Ffootage clearly showed him at the
OL,14,Ffront of the disorder, and then
OL,15,Fthrowing rocks and smashing the door
OL,16,Fof the TK Maxx store on Royal Parade.
OL,18,FHe pleaded guilty to committing
OL,19,Fviolent disorder and criminal damage
OL,20,Fand was jailed for 32 months at
OL,21,FPlymouth Crown Court today.
