OL,3,C'I was just a drunk idiot' - Men face
OL,4,C'day of reckoning' after violent scenes
OL,6,FCrimp, of Palace Street, Plymouth, was
OL,7,Finvolved in unruly scenes on Monday
OL,8,Fand was responsible for causing damage
OL,9,Fto property valued over #5000.
OL,11,FHe was arrested at his home address on
OL,12,FWednesday 7 August 2024 after footage
OL,13,Fgathered by Devon & Cornwall Police
OL,14,Fwas used to identify Crimp. Charges
OL,15,Fwere authorised at 3.30am on 8 August
OL,16,F2024, by CPS Direct.
