OL,3,C'I was just a drunk idiot' - Men face
OL,4,C'day of reckoning' after violent scenes
OL,6,FVictoria Cook, Chief Crown Prosecutor
OL,7,Ffor the South West, said: "Justin
OL,8,FCrimp acted disgracefully during the
OL,9,Fcollective disorder in Plymouth on
OL,10,FMonday. By involving himself in the
OL,11,Funrest and causing destruction to a
OL,12,Fhigh street store, he has showed an
OL,13,Futter disregard for his community.
OL,15,F"Hundreds of prosecutors have been
OL,16,Fworking around the clock across the
OL,17,FCrown Prosecution Service, making
OL,18,Frapid charging decisions so that
OL,19,Fsuspects can be brought before the
OL,20,Fcourts without delay.
